              "description": "Dedicate time to a Python crash course, focusing on variable declaration, basic data types (integers, floats, strings, booleans), and arithmetic/logical operators. The objective is to write short scripts that demonstrate understanding of these core concepts, laying the groundwork for more complex programming.",
