              "description": "Engage in your first High-Intensity Interval Training (HIIT) session, focusing on short bursts of intense exercise followed by brief recovery periods. Design a 30-minute routine incorporating bodyweight exercises like burpees, jumping jacks, and mountain climbers, pushing your cardiovascular limits to improve endurance and metabolic rate. Monitor your heart rate to stay within target zones.",
