              "title": "LeetCode/HackerRank: Easy Array/String Problem",
              "description": "Tackle an easy-level problem on LeetCode or HackerRank that involves array or string manipulation. Focus on optimizing your solution for time and space complexity, using Python's built-in data structures efficiently. Time yourself to improve problem-solving speed and logical thinking under constraints.",
