              "title": "Weekly Review: ML Baseline Performance & Feature Engineering",
              "description": "Conduct a comprehensive review of Week 4. Analyze the performance of your baseline ML models and critically evaluate the effectiveness of your feature engineering and preprocessing steps. Reflect on how different choices impacted model results. Document lessons learned and outline areas for algorithmic improvement next week. This iterative process is core to ML engineering.",
