              "description": "Introduce Principal Component Analysis (PCA), a technique for reducing the dimensionality of datasets while preserving most of the variance. Understand its use in feature extraction and noise reduction. Implement PCA using `sklearn.decomposition` and visualize data in reduced dimensions. This can improve model training speed and reduce complexity.",
