              "description": "Actively seek skill endorsements from colleagues or connections on LinkedIn for relevant technical skills (Python, ML, Data Analysis). Also, consider requesting recommendations from professors, mentors, or past supervisors, providing them with clear prompts about what you'd like them to highlight. This strengthens your professional credibility.",
