              "title": "Advanced ML: Gradient Boosting (XGBoost/LightGBM) Introduction",
              "description": "Introduce yourself to Gradient Boosting machines, specifically XGBoost or LightGBM, which are highly optimized and widely used algorithms. Understand the concept of boosting and how these libraries improve upon traditional gradient boosting. Read introductory articles and explore basic usage of one of these libraries for a classification or regression task. These are crucial for winning ML competitions.",
