              "title": "MLOps Concepts: Model Versioning & Experiment Tracking",
              "description": "Explore foundational MLOps concepts: model versioning (e.g., using DVC or simply Git for small models) and experiment tracking (e.g., MLflow, Weights & Biases). Understand why these practices are essential for reproducible and manageable ML workflows in production environments. Research tools and their benefits. This bridges the gap between ML research and engineering.",
