              "description": "Design and execute a hybrid circuit training session that combines strength exercises with short bursts of cardio. For example, 5 strength exercises followed by 1 minute of jump rope, repeated 3-4 times. This maximizes caloric expenditure and improves both muscular endurance and cardiovascular fitness. Track repetitions and circuit completion times.",
