              "title": "Portfolio Project: Implement XGBoost/LightGBM Model",
              "description": "Integrate an XGBoost or LightGBM model into your portfolio project. Compare its performance against your previously trained models, leveraging its advanced boosting capabilities. Document the model's configuration, training process, and evaluation metrics in your Jupyter Notebook. This demonstrates proficiency in state-of-the-art ML algorithms.",
