              "description": "Prepare a short presentation (5-7 minutes) on your portfolio project's findings, focusing on key insights and model performance. Develop a few simple visual aids (e.g., a chart of model accuracies, a key graph from EDA). Practice delivering the presentation, incorporating your visual aids effectively. This improves your ability to convey complex information visually.",
