              "description": "Research Continuous Integration/Continuous Deployment (CI/CD) concepts specifically in the context of Machine Learning. Understand how automated testing and deployment pipelines ensure code quality and seamless model updates. Explore tools like GitHub Actions, GitLab CI/CD, or Jenkins for ML workflows. This introduces you to a critical aspect of MLOps.",
