              "description": "Engage in a Zone 2 cardio session, incorporating slight resistance or elevation (e.g., inclined treadmill, cycling with higher gear). This subtly increases the challenge while maintaining the target heart rate zone, enhancing cardiovascular adaptation. Aim for 45-60 minutes, monitoring heart rate and perceived effort. This is a progression from prior Zone 2 sessions.",
