              "description": "Practice single-tasking for at least two major tasks today, dedicating your full attention to one activity without switching context. Turn off notifications and close irrelevant tabs. Measure the quality and speed of your work compared to multitasking. This method, contrary to common belief, significantly boosts deep work capability.",
