              "description": "Explore the concept of model serving and how machine learning models are deployed into production environments via APIs. Research frameworks like Flask, FastAPI, or TensorFlow Serving. Understand the need for robust, scalable, and low-latency inference. This is a core AI engineering skill for bringing models to users.",
