              "description": "Develop a customizable cover letter template that highlights your skills, enthusiasm for AI/ML, and career aspirations. Include sections for a strong opening, body paragraphs linking your experience to job requirements, and a compelling closing. Focus on making it adaptable for various roles while maintaining a personal touch. This accelerates job application processes.",
