              "description": "Formally initiate the project by defining the high-level problem statement. This involves brainstorming potential computer vision tasks for a major hackathon (e.g., specific object detection, fine-grained classification, anomaly detection) and outlining the desired impact. Identify 3-5 potential problem statements to research further. This initial framing sets the direction for subsequent research and development.",
