              "title": "Define Core Problem & Scope",
              "description": "Formulate a precise problem statement for the computer vision pipeline. This involves identifying a specific challenge, for example, 'real-time detection of specific objects in an industrial setting' or 'fine-grained classification of plant diseases from mobile images,' and detailing the expected output format (e.g., bounding boxes, class labels). Clearly articulate the scope, identifying what the system will and will not attempt to achieve, to ensure focused development for the hackathon.",
