              "description": "Conduct an initial search for existing solutions, datasets, and common approaches to the defined problem. Focus on recent advancements (last 2-3 years) in relevant conferences like CVPR, ICCV, ECCV, and journals. Prioritize papers that address similar modalities or application contexts, extracting key architectural patterns and performance benchmarks.",
