              "description": "Set up a dedicated Python virtual environment using Anaconda/Miniconda or `venv` to manage dependencies. Create a `requirements.txt` file listing essential packages like `numpy`, `pandas`, `matplotlib`, and `jupyter`. This isolation prevents conflicts with other projects and ensures reproducible dependency management.",
