              "title": "Review Week 1 Progress & Plan for Week 2",
              "description": "Assess accomplishments against Week 1 objectives, noting any deviations or unexpected challenges. Prepare a detailed plan for Week 2 focusing on deepening CV fundamentals, refining dataset strategy, and setting up experiment tracking. Ensure all foundational setups are stable before moving forward.",
