              "description": "Based on initial research and CV fundamentals, refine the problem statement to include technical constraints and performance targets. For example, specify target inference latency (e.g., <50ms per image), minimum accuracy (e.g., >90% mAP), and hardware limitations. This makes the goal more concrete and measurable.",
