              "id": "mqtsslvqjbyi0",
              "title": "Implement Optical Flow (Lucas-Kanade concepts)",
              "description": "Explore the concept of optical flow for motion estimation. Understand how `cv2.calcOpticalFlowPyrLK()` tracks features across frames. Implement a basic optical flow visualization. While not always directly used in static image CV, it provides insight into dynamic scene analysis, relevant for video processing.",
