              "description": "Learn about background subtraction techniques like MOG2 (`cv2.createBackgroundSubtractorMOG2`) and KNN (`cv2.createBackgroundSubtractorKNN`). Implement these algorithms on a short video sequence to segment moving foreground objects from a static background. This is useful for surveillance or activity monitoring applications.",
