              "title": "Deep Dive: Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) Fundamentals",
              "description": "Study the core concepts of Convolutional Neural Networks: convolution layers, activation functions (ReLU), pooling layers (max, average), and fully connected layers. Understand how CNNs automatically learn hierarchical features from images. This theoretical foundation is paramount for deep learning-based vision systems.",
