              "title": "Implement Advanced Data Cleaning: Annotation Consistency Checks",
              "description": "Enhance the data quality check script to include advanced annotation consistency checks. This involves looking for very small or extremely large bounding boxes (potential errors), out-of-bounds annotations, and verifying class label integrity against a predefined list. Flag anomalies for manual review.",
