              "description": "Install and configure the chosen data augmentation library (e.g., Albumentations). Define an initial augmentation pipeline including transformations like random horizontal flips, shifts, rotations, brightness/contrast adjustments, and mild noise injection. Test the pipeline with sample images to visualize effects.",
