              "title": "Configure Experiment Tracking for Baseline Run",
              "description": "Set up the experiment tracking system (MLflow/W&B) for the first baseline run. Log all model hyperparameters, optimizer settings, loss function choice, and data augmentation parameters. Initialize a new experiment run for this baseline, ensuring clear naming (e.g., 'Baseline_Model_V1').",
